{"tid":1499583,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"無線耳機 Nuarl NT100AX 用後感","createTime":"2019-08-23T18:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T12:11:22.000Z","uid":104171,"like":7,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"a8bd5134d58f29e0115d0bbdbdd48373b21c0e4f","tid":1499583,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:27:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y0FOj9D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy0FOj9D.jpg&h=6590c4ec&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有 fd 叫我幫手 post:<br />\n<br />\n話說呢排睇緊真無線耳機，想分享下點樣試耳機。<br />\n<br />\n喺豐澤試戴過Jabra Elite Active 65t，感覺戴入耳仔好實，加上佢個耳機機身形狀令佢個重心落得較近耳仔，狂 fing 個頭都唔會鬆，而且貼耳令到隔聲做得唔錯。<br />\n<br />\n但最後無買到Jabra<br />\n1. 切換去聽街外聲音嘅時候，覺得唔係好聽到，始終都係要除一邊落黎<br />\n2. 較大細聲嘅按鈕唔方便，唔係撳一下就得，要摸中個大聲按鈕/細聲按鈕先得<br />\n<br />\n然後去左旺角星際，有間 <span style=\"color: red;\">KINGSOUND「金聲耳筒」</span>好好人，由我試耳機試咗粒幾鐘都有，完全無黑面仲有傾有講。一開始試咗 1more 同 Sudio，比較下發覺 1more 個 base 太重喇，聽電音ok，但係我聽歌有人唱嘅唔想比d配樂蓋過，而 Sudio 人聲比較出。同埋除咗聽歌仲會聽電台或者睇 Youtube，<span style=\"color: red;\">base太大聲會好影響覺得好「宏」</span>。<br />\n<br />\n然後同店主傾幾句，佢推薦咗 Nuarl nt100ax。所以就將 Nuarl 同 Sudio 比較。<br />\n<br />\nNuarl 明顯大舊過 Sudio，耳機顏色、樣貌、穩固程度都遜於 Sudio。Sudio 耳機重心比較貼耳，狂 fing 個頭都唔會甩，而 Nuarl 重心比較離耳，fing完會有d鬆。但係!!!!!!! Nuarl 嘅聲極之靚，長期聽都唔會有「宏」嘅感覺，而且人聲好細膩清晰，Sudio人聲已經好好但相比下 Sudio 始終比較沙啞。而且，<span style=\"color: red;\">大家聽歌都一定會不其然較大聲咗，聽得耐會好「宏」，會想較細聲d，但細聲咗又享受唔到。</span>而 Nuarl 較得大聲d都唔會有呢個問題，歌嘅樂器聽到非常清澈仔細，例如 iu 嘅歌背景小提琴同鋼琴聲，Sudio 較大聲黎聽係會有好粗糙嘅小提琴聲，而 Nuarl係好銳利好仔細嘅，好真實，真係好靚聲。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以最後都係買咗 Nuarl。</span><br />\n<br />\n順帶一提，途中仲試聽咗 Nakamichi TW2 plus 同 Lypertek Tevi，比較下 Nakamichi 比較好，同樣地係比 Lypertek 無咁「宏」，人聲突出，無比 base 蓋過。但 Nakamichi 嘅聲，仔細度同銳利程度都唔及 Nuarl。<br />\n<br />\n個人得出排名 (用途為聽歌、聽Youtube、電台):<br />\nNuarl &gt; Sudio &gt; Jabra &gt; Nakamichi &gt; 1more &gt; Lypertek<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8X1Rh7V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8X1Rh7V.jpg&h=2acf0716&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nNakamichi<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NwLVKNL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNwLVKNL.jpg&h=b3417203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nLypertek<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DZFCdGG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDZFCdGG.jpg&h=ef2df1ab&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n1more<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z62hdG2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ62hdG2.jpg&h=b00cd60e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSudio tolv"},{"pid":"c9748dde3c12a91f00412577ee94655a7728f235","tid":1499583,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:28:18.000Z","msg":"sorry 標題打錯<br />\n係<span style=\"color: red;\">nuarl nt01ax</span>"},{"pid":"bac597fcdd69e4180ffc6d9f6714b37b23b22459","tid":1499583,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:30:55.000Z","msg":"幾錢"},{"pid":"83de4b8dc690a54551a1bedbcbedd6ef3fdc02be","tid":1499583,"uid":89514,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"efbe36d145d2413899b780d8132c64488332b067","tid":1499583,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"83de4b8dc690a54551a1bedbcbedd6ef3fdc02be","tid":1499583,"uid":89514,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"quote":{"pid":"bac597fcdd69e4180ffc6d9f6714b37b23b22459","tid":1499583,"uid":14075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:30:55.000Z","msg":"幾錢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T18:47:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:29:54.000Z","msg":"好幽默喎你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bc48caeb35f362ee2a0d1a3948c24ec60103a37","tid":1499583,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T11:13:46.000Z","msg":"用心試完，寫用後感<br />\n無人理